{"tid":746491,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【少圖少字】日本長野快閃兩日兩夜聖巡","createTime":"2018-07-17T14:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T11:36:45.000Z","uid":151677,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1e9ec8f4711c737a6c1ad9a5ae76a73577bac070","tid":746491,"uid":151677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:50:53.000Z","msg":"今年6月頭小弟去左日本玩個零禮拜，幾中有兩日去左長野諏訪聖巡yuru camp 同你的名字<br />\n呢個post應該只會講嗰兩日嘅行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兩日都只係去左兩個地方，一個係霧峰高原，一個係諏訪市內嘅立石公園同諏訪湖<br />\n先上圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/185124_902857203c6cfe868c59d50de2472155.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F185124_902857203c6cfe868c59d50de2472155.png&h=249889d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/185125_5e6682ffe62b63c00f5db4933bc9e8c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F185125_5e6682ffe62b63c00f5db4933bc9e8c0.png&h=dd8a99ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/185126_4cf1c3915ed168fcb8f761103d867f70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F185126_4cf1c3915ed168fcb8f761103d867f70.png&h=f3948484&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/185127_22b9bbf62b777f88b456edaf71eb6c5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F185127_22b9bbf62b777f88b456edaf71eb6c5b.png&h=70be11c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/185133_18b80bedd20f662656dc6fefe7461613.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F185133_18b80bedd20f662656dc6fefe7461613.png&h=68812bc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"618076d