1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"夜晚喺新宿坐車去到諏訪市住左晚網吧<br />\n一朝早就去今晚住嘅油店到放低行李<br />\n然後喺7仔買啲野食野飲<br />\n就去jr站隔離搭巴士出發去霧峰高原<br />\n<br />\n上到巴士，得一個乘客⋯<br />\n於是成程車都係得我同一個婆婆,唔通鄉下地方真係冇人...<br />\n架巴士係咁減速轉彎同上斜，所以都有啲辛苦<br />\n上到山腰部手機仲要變埋圈外(下次應該要買一張收得好啲嘅電話卡)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再坐多廿分鐘，終於到左霧峰高原<br />\n一落車，見到藍天白雲同一大片草原<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/122115_3854834715153f2574b97c3f8efde589.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F122115_3854834715153f2574b97c3f8efde589.JPG&h=7b7ba951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/122127_04a63ae6091cd9be19ef7a40e805ad83.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F122127_04a63ae6091cd9be19ef7a40e805ad83.JPG&h=944957a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/123635_36055ad701eb27ebd2ae6e262487aba9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F123635_36055ad701eb27ebd2ae6e262487aba9.JPG&h=dd282795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢到大概就係主角上山嗰度, 但我冇影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/123625_16332681f7b49f9cb613a342fcbc76e8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F123625_16332681f7b49f9cb613a342fcbc76e8.JPG&h=10a2df1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/123334_1d17cabde68264831ad6bc96e1802092.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F123334_1d17cabde68264831ad6bc96e1802092.jpg&h=3597ab2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/122320_b7150b9ab52cd081fcbc9e0ba3b98d95.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F122320_b7150b9ab52cd081fcbc9e0ba3b98d95.JPG&h=4f9c6a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/122357_62b5f1776bb425de5e030e4fa44c55a7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F122357_62b5f1776bb425de5e030e4fa44c55a7.JPG&h=7fa9f21b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行左十分鐘先意識到自己行左上條馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行多個零鐘先見到有啲建築物，就入去兜下<br />\nyuru camp入面女主食過嗰間cafe(?) 原來就係度<br />\n一碗似羅宋湯嘅紅菜頭湯，加多兩個餐包就1000羊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/123501_82c761f19840e38cc87c2b63dd602261.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F123501_82c761f19840e38cc87c2b63dd602261.JPG&h=1750cca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但又真係幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野食我俾8/10<br />\n加埋個景我俾11/10！<br />\n<br />\n食飽就開始上路"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:37:15.000Z","msg":"個湯咩味，係咪港式嗰隻味&hellip;？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d962e7535af3bf59a3f7e36d7fd23567268ed13","tid":746491,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"我聽日都去諏訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56663979e5c54edfe1a8bfa608219178e318fdff","tid":746491,"uid":151677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4053c52b917ac165e30f8b7108f97bc826c81b43","tid":746491,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56a3da72716001be209f4d76db0692b6e5639f54","tid":746491,"uid":151677,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"夜晚喺新宿坐車去到諏訪市住左晚網吧<br />\n一朝早就去今晚住嘅油店到放低行李<br />\n然後喺7仔買啲野食野飲<br />\n就去jr站隔離搭巴士出發去霧峰高原<br />\n<br />\n上到巴士，得一個乘客⋯<br />\n於是成程車都係得我同一個婆婆,唔通鄉下地方真係冇人...<br />\n架巴士係咁減速轉彎同上斜，所以都有啲辛苦<br />\n上到山腰部手機仲要變埋圈外(下次應該要買一張收得好啲嘅電話卡)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再坐多廿分鐘，終於到左霧峰高原<br />\n一落車，見到藍天白雲同一大片草原<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/122115_3854834715153f2574b97c3f8efde589.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F122115_3854834715153f2574b97c3f8efde589.JPG&h=7b7ba951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/122127_04a63ae6091cd9be19ef7a40e805ad83.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F122127_04a63ae6091cd9be19ef7a40e805ad83.JPG&h=944957a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/123635_36055ad701eb27ebd2ae6e262487aba9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F123635_36055ad701eb27ebd2ae6e262487aba9.JPG&h=dd282795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢到大概就係主角上山嗰度, 但我冇影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/123625_16332681f7b49f9cb613a342fcbc76e8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F123625_16332681f7b49f9cb613a342fcbc76e8.JPG&h=10a2df1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/123334_1d17cabde68264831ad6bc96e1802092.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F123334_1d17cabde68264831ad6bc96e1802092.jpg&h=3597ab2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/122320_b7150b9ab52cd081fcbc9e0ba3b98d95.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F122320_b7150b9ab52cd081fcbc9e0ba3b98d95.JPG&h=4f9c6a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/122357_62b5f1776bb425de5e030e4fa44c55a7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F122357_62b5f1776bb425de5e030e4fa44c55a7.JPG&h=7fa9f21b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行左十分鐘先意識到自己行左上條馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行多個零鐘先見到有啲建築物，就入去兜下<br />\nyuru camp入面女主食過嗰間cafe(?) 原來就係度<br />\n一碗似羅宋湯嘅紅菜頭湯，加多兩個餐包就1000羊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/123501_82c761f19840e38cc87c2b63dd602261.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F123501_82c761f19840e38cc87c2b63dd602261.JPG&h=1750cca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但又真係幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野食我俾8/10<br />\n加埋個景我俾11/10！<br />\n<br />\n食飽就開始上路"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:37:15.000Z","msg":"個湯咩味，係咪港式嗰隻味&hellip;？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T17:35:36.000Z","msg":"梗係好飲好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb25407f61823736ea6425b695aa2c98a6ce7f8a","tid":746491,"uid":151677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d962e7535af3bf59a3f7e36d7fd23567268ed13","tid":746491,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"我聽日都去諏訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"記住黃昏嗰時先上去影相<br />\n應該靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d53d04bba5e5b711e2381b401dc97c193866f2b","tid":746491,"uid":43545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"上年都去左立石<br />\n<br />\n其實日落去都靚，當然無動畫咁震撼啦大佬<br />\nYuyu camp 係係法師山果邊望返落去，天氣好可以睇到富士山<br />\n網上有d 相睇到幾靚，不過唔揸車都幾難去"},{"pid":"e283307861568a6157fd3791b431f18f8d3150a5","tid":746491,"uid":32645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d53d04bba5e5b711e2381b401dc97c193866f2b","tid":746491,"uid":43545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"上年都去左立石<br />\n<br />\n其實日落去都靚，當然無動畫咁震撼啦大佬<br />\nYuyu camp 係係法師山果邊望返落去，天氣好可以睇到富士山<br />\n網上有d 相睇到幾靚，不過唔揸車都幾難去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:54:15.000Z","msg":"我就係去法師山果邊<br />\n不過係行過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重要係行夜山<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e85b74cca8d44d3bc5f51a7625b86665fcb6c5f","tid":746491,"uid":43545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e283307861568a6157fd3791b431f18f8d3150a5","tid":746491,"uid":32645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d53d04bba5e5b711e2381b401dc97c193866f2b","tid":746491,"uid":43545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"上年都去左立石<br />\n<br />\n其實日落去都靚，當然無動畫咁震撼啦大佬<br />\nYuyu camp 係係法師山果邊望返落去，天氣好可以睇到富士山<br />\n網上有d 相睇到幾靚，不過唔揸車都幾難去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:54:15.000Z","msg":"我就係去法師山果邊<br />\n不過係行過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重要係行夜山<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:18:33.000Z","msg":"行左幾耐，本來諗過租一日車上去，見JR 租車都唔貴<br />\n但驚夜路山路，放棄左"},{"pid":"5e2cc2b9f54b34ed5aa96250c09131ee6e360cea","tid":746491,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e85b74cca8d44d3bc5f51a7625b86665fcb6c5f","tid":746491,"uid":43545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e283307861568a6