5426581&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/091722_f79597e4f986617207f3d550eb91a010.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F091722_f79597e4f986617207f3d550eb91a010.png&h=3fe2dce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為網速慢到連唔到google map<br />\n所以又要問人路<br />\n咁岩前面就有兩個老人家，就問佢地去車山（即係山頂）係咪呢條路，佢地又話得呢條路<br />\n咁唯有死死氣繼續行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/091742_2c6d1b9581d8a9c0b3c5c984b21b790a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F091742_2c6d1b9581d8a9c0b3c5c984b21b790a.png&h=78166255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再行多大半個鐘終於到車山，呢到真係好似3號波咁大風<br />\n然後就喺度瘋狂影相<br />\n（又要咁岩俾我影到富士山）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/091821_07a4a8622d85ef2c864a4a3faaefafb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F091821_07a4a8622d85ef2c864a4a3faaefafb3.png&h=cd4d3517&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/091822_4fda058096ee8cb06eb7f14ca329b3bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F091822_4fda058096ee8cb06eb7f14ca329b3bc.png&h=409e1148&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/091824_3ec2fdf41c439ddc9b4ba9d3a424f284.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F091824_3ec2fdf41c439ddc9b4ba9d3a424f284.png&h=7a8e8044&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/091826_655af9dd3bbad970a7e91a65a540779d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F091826_655af9dd3bbad970a7e91a65a540779d.png&h=e1368284&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/091827_57e6aa4ed2267deeaf395cd49f3645c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F091827_57e6aa4ed2267deeaf395cd49f3645c1.png&h=452b7415&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/091829_ef96ae7950781e86a6f67c9861e20637.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F091829_ef96ae7950781e86a6f67c9861e20637.png&h=2e51d8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/091831_b061b6a7b363b2e209bb895c682138b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F091831_b061b6a7b363b2e209bb895c682138b4.png&h=d9ec8d84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/091832_54824b9ceb0d05a9ee6ea0262c76b4ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F091832_54824b9ceb0d05a9ee6ea0262c76b4ad.png&h=7514ad7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/092004_0bf26d48c8cc5497dadc7f14a67197dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F092004_0bf26d48c8cc5497dadc7f14a67197dc.png&h=73ae19fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影完就直接俾1000羊坐纜車落山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實在太攰唔想行落山<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/092031_d935110841507691f68ee32cb31d3b44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F092031_d935110841507691f68ee32cb31d3b44.png&h=79e85cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落到去，發覺呢到都係冇巴士出翻去，於是又要行石路落去白樺湖嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/092057_172e2087c047245e838cc157d20325f6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F092057_172e2087c047245e838cc157d20325f6.png&h=e3f4e113&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/092059_bc252970d9e49a73aa8b4ef9bb8561ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F092059_bc252970d9e49a73aa8b4ef9bb8561ec.png&h=cb64a631&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/092101_236223f7d91b0ed4f89da98c2c20370f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F092101_236223f7d91b0ed4f89da98c2c20370f.png&h=6fa7949d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個時候我發覺自己手臂同頸有啲痛（強烈建議大家搽防曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n白樺湖西面有一半都係廢置嘅建築，因為趕巴士就冇咩點影，下次如果再黎可以去埋東面個牧場飲下奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/092136_ee0ae0f735e633ac34b5a0137f38ebf3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F092136_ee0ae0f735e633ac34b5a0137f38ebf3.png&h=f96841a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/092137_469da52dfa8b66d85cb121cea3ecf9c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F092137_469da52dfa8b66d85cb121cea3ecf9c1.png&h=cd4db1c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐巴士落到茅野，再轉電車返諏訪<br />\n呢個時候已經攰到仆街<br />\n原本諗住襯黃昏上埋立石公園，但最後都係冇去<br />\n(之後好撚後悔冇上埋去)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 電車站內竟然有個足湯（冇圖）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n浸左陣就返酒店龜縮左成晚"},{"pid":"5aab434540c8613cbd56a8b68f5a5dd740870f43","tid":746491,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:28:44.000Z","msg":"死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f683f9391d2a04a76c3cbc102a81eb2d63834956","tid":746491,"uid":151677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:29:15.000Z","msg":"大家係咪以為已經出完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342a7e18ef9a9ed691ae2259270cedd2082c8c0b","tid":746491,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:33:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad70f7f7c568fe2c3566370ea33d1521daaf7407","tid":746491,"uid":8017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:55:22.000Z","msg":"點睇到樓主係morning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2659c79523413ee5f916d68b950ef31a49e276d","tid":746491,"uid":8017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad70f7f7c568fe2c3566370ea33d1521daaf7407","tid":746491,"uid":8017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:55:22.000Z","msg":"點睇到樓主係morning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"Mk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3746078efd5a582efb291daa6ecf6477a3268b52","tid":746491,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"巴打與唔覺得諏訪喱個城市好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590aeb7be07ef03b2b68eceabe777a693f15422c","tid":746491,"uid":151677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3746078efd5a582efb291daa6ecf6477a3268b52","tid":746491,"uid":32645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"巴打與唔覺得諏訪喱個城市好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T08:38:22.000Z","msg":"Why<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f403718ee67c1fc2e5a43bfdde5d4ce4780a27","tid":746491,"uid":151677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T08:52:01.000Z","msg":"一早起身執好野就落樓擺行李再去行山上立石公園<br />\n事前唔知原來樓梯仲多過斜路，琴日行完山又未恢復體力，搞到中途都抖左兩獲<br />\n冇預過上立石公園會咁攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肥宅上到山嗰下feel到就死<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164328_b821223dfcf936736c5046de0dae888a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164328_b821223dfcf936736c5046de0dae888a.png&h=07c81945&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164329_01b7dc47c0c333ac0ebf2749f678069b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164329_01b7dc47c0c333ac0ebf2749f678069b.png&h=b0706668&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164330_2ed89512e6819302b05df156ac75dabb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164330_2ed89512e6819302b05df156ac75dabb.png&h=d9773c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上到黎即刻播返首前前前世黎聽<br />\n一路聽一路影相<br />\n黎到呢到又諗起你的名字入面某幾個畫面...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164421_4fec908b865547d79c44a6aa9c0261f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164421_4fec908b865547d79c44a6aa9c0261f5.png&h=532a7805&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164422_e402adc2aa2902d7dfcf5b03579cf884.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164422_e402adc2aa2902d7dfcf5b03579cf884.png&h=4cf8fd1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164424_ebec7389213284b936b6ae2eedbbf4af.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164424_ebec7389213284b936b6ae2eedbbf4af.png&h=519c45c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留意到就算係接近中午時候都好多日本人黎影相<br />\n諏訪湖真係好靚，又萬里無雲,好清楚可以望到好遠嗰幾坐山<br />\n不枉我千里迢迢由東京⋯呀唔係，由香港過到黎長野<br />\n上埋個觀景台打卡(好似冬天會唔開)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164532_053e1e2560846fddba02b95d8b663df0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164532_053e1e2560846fddba02b95d8b663df0.png&h=8d3c71c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164533_9ba8b61fae701e162d7ccff8aa8df2d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164533_9ba8b61fae701e162d7ccff8aa8df2d7.png&h=83ebc779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影完就行第二條路落山,意外發現個發電廠<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164607_e5154f83e2d29df57ae06d675c885a11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164607_e5154f83e2d29df57ae06d675c885a11.png&h=d2c38800&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164609_fb600a1f6207a7b5fcccd15ff2dcc614.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164609_fb600a1f6207a7b5fcccd15ff2dcc614.png&h=54aa5ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同電影入面嗰個發電廠真係幾似<br />\n<br />\n落山之後就諗住去湖邊兜下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164734_19f939d65fa84dc9bdea51423dcb6f45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164734_19f939d65fa84dc9bdea51423dcb6f45.png&h=c5e94395&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/164735_871fca8994ce8f7a0a18f25766e5dcde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F164735_871fca8994ce8f7a0a18f25766e5dcde.png&h=592cceec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再行多陣等到夠鐘就去返車站嗰邊搭高速巴士走<br />\n長野都係一個好地方黎嘅，如果有機會都想冬天再黎多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n估唔到得嗰幾篇野我都可以拖咁耐先出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway多謝睇到最後一篇嘅你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完！"}]}